msgid ""
"Supported formats: GeoTIFF, JPEG, and PNG with GDAL PAM metadata (.aux.xml "
"files). Multi-file datasets should be uploaded as ZIP archives."
msgstr ""
"פורמטים נתמכים: GeoTIFF, JPEG ו-PNG עם מטא-נתונים של GDAL PAM (קבצי "
